{"tid":1599490,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「popo 睇路」太公報擬「十一殺警」令国慶變港殤","createTime":"2019-09-28T04:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T09:36:22.000Z","uid":263448,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a6578081495015c962662084e248d196dbcdc52","tid":1599490,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzROBQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzROBQB.jpg&h=77936508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太公報已經寫好小說劇本，等10月1日国慶，就會幫升級警方升級至實彈射殺，同時升級示威者道德底線。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">示威者明知警方殺咗唔少香港人，都未見過砍斷警方手手腳腳，最多打佢一身。</span><br />\n<br />\n警方一直話香港人係「曱甴」，早前仲話維尼忍唔到10月後，依家101太公突然又話要「殺警」，再加上日前員佐級話要用「實彈鎮壓」，明顯係想為「屠殺港人」開路。<br />\n<br />\n即是咁，警隊明顯收到上頭話唔可以明面殺人，只能暗殺。但暗殺包唔住，示威又無減少，中共一直搵方法想示威升級，等示威者殺警先。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我懷疑案發時間會係10月2日0時0分左右，盡量避免接近10月1。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得警察無明面殺人，示威者好難暗殺警員。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要令101變国殤，唯一方法係將101變成警員殘殺市民，而唔係示威者殺死警員。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以警察自己睇路，由其係覺得自己白果啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb31fd24ba708e7dcdad9375403437d5752f62a","tid":1599490,"uid":117276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"冇聽過<br />\n不過港共聽過破窗效應未<br />\n有第一隻狗仔死,其他都好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bce5273713b8aa02c6ed251a11fe4dbbd5b1913","tid":1599490,"uid":170445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:39:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b30f5c16726c9dc50491738d08c09986c5ba4fc","tid":1599490,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"白痴黑警，由頭到尾以為示威者想殺你<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味隨時最後係你支持嘅大陸/香港政府收你皮<br />\n<br />\n做黑警變左做烈士，笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27d662f7d9453e340d74fb909c023acf0d21e49","tid":1599490,"uid":87552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"所羅門已經知道呢個劇本<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqyM9pu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqyM9pu.png&h=adee0ca9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef2aef287d018685a0def40bbc741f2672b9a729","tid":1599490,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"殺乜警啫，呢啲叫天譴"},{"pid":"f01504a4a8c904f4e855c401252eaa0b2f55d797","tid":1599490,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:10:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"411cc0302e74a689f81c482692c55b133de2f4ea","tid":1599490,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2adbba623bda634417c5ac8a57396e48583b8f9a","tid":1599490,"uid":251074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T09:36:22.000Z","msg":"問左大大未先。。。。捉到就算係唔係休班及有任務，當天一定會被condom"}]}